title: The Gothic Image - Religious Art in France of the 13th Century
description:
The Gothic Image: Religious Art in France of the Thirteenth Century
Harper & Brothers Publishers | 1958 | ISBN: N/A | English | 456 pages | PDF | 68.2 MB

Emile Male's great book is basic for the understanding of medieval art and medieval symbolism, and of the vision of the world which presided over the building of the French cathedrals. It is an indispensable guide for the student of Western culture
